imdb.plot outline: Gallery of Guns Television brings the home shopping concept to you. Watch Bo Keister & Anne-Marie Rhodes explain and demonstrate many firearms from the world's leading manufacturers such as Ruger, Taurus, FNH USA, Mossberg, Browning, Smith & Wesson, and many others. The show's themed episodes are designed to help you make informed buying decisions and provide you with an ultra-convenient way to purchase firearms online.
